PrecisAuthorization to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of NOVA SCOTIA in order to compensate it for payments made to producers under provincial agricultural risk management programs which had the effect of reducing the federal share of payments under the Agriculture Income Disaster Assistance (AIDA) Program in 1998 and 1999.
Attachments
precis:
Authorization to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of NOVA SCOTIA
in order to compensate it for payments made to producers under provincial
agricultural risk management programs which had the effect of reducing the
federal share of payments under the Agriculture Income Disaster Assistance
(AIDA) Program in 1998 and 1999.
